14namespace detail {
15
16template <template <typename> typename F, typename List>
17struct map_impl;
18template <template <typename> typename F, typename... Ts>
19struct map_impl<F, list<Ts...>> {
20 using type = list<typename F<Ts>::type...>;
21};
22
23template <typename List, typename T, int NotFoundIndex, int I>
24struct find_first_impl;
25template <typename Head, typename... Tail, typename T, int NotFoundIndex, int I>
26struct find_first_impl<list<Head, Tail...>, T, NotFoundIndex, I>
27 : find_first_impl<list<Tail...>, T, NotFoundIndex, I + 1> {};
28template <typename... Tail, typename T, int NotFoundIndex, int I>
29struct find_first_impl<list<T, Tail...>, T, NotFoundIndex, I>
30 : std::integral_constant<int, I> {};
31template <typename T, int NotFoundIndex, int I>
32struct find_first_impl<list<>, T, NotFoundIndex, I>
33 : std::integral_constant<int, NotFoundIndex> {};
34
35template <typename List, template <typename, typename> typename Cmp>
36struct all_equal_impl;
37template <typename Head, typename... Tail,
38 template <typename, typename> typename Cmp>
39struct all_equal_impl<list<Head, Tail...>, Cmp>
40 : std::bool_constant<(Cmp<Head, Tail>::value && ...)> {};
41
42} // namespace detail
43
44// map<F, List>::type is a new list after applying {F} (in the form of
45// F<E>::type) to all elements (E) in {List}.
46template <template <typename> typename F, typename List>
47struct map : detail::map_impl<F, List> {};
48template <template <typename> typename F, typename List>
49using map_t = typename map<F, List>::type;
50
51// find_first<List, T, NotFoundIndex = -1>::value is the index of the first
52// occurrence of {T} in {List} or otherwise {NotFoundIndex}.
53template <typename List, typename T, int NotFoundIndex = -1>
54struct find_first : detail::find_first_impl<List, T, NotFoundIndex, 0> {};
55template <typename List, typename T, int NotFoundIndex = -1>
56constexpr int find_first_v = find_first<List, T, NotFoundIndex>::value;
57
58// contains<List, T>::value is true iff {List} contains {T}.
59template <typename List, typename T>
60struct contains : std::bool_constant<find_first<List, T, -1>::value != -1> {};
61template <typename List, typename T>
62constexpr int contains_v = contains<List, T>::value;
63
64// all_equal<List, Cmp = std::is_same>::value is true iff all values in {List}
65// are equal with respect to {Cmp}.
66template <typename List,
67 template <typename, typename> typename Cmp = std::is_same>
68struct all_equal : detail::all_equal_impl<List, Cmp> {};
69template <typename List,
70 template <typename, typename> typename Cmp = std::is_same>
71constexpr bool all_equal_v = all_equal<List, Cmp>::value;
72
73} // namespace v8::base::tmp
